Carbon coefficient data sourced from BEDEC/ITeC (Institut de Tecnologia de la
Construcció de Catalunya) via the 2050-materials API. Data is used for
educational and research purposes under the terms of the respective data
providers. Users are responsible for verifying data accuracy for any
professional or regulatory application.

This tool was developed as an academic research project at IAAC Barcelona and
is not intended as a substitute for professional LCA assessment or regulatory
compliance advice.
